    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow under 350 capacity venues to reopen with Covid-secure guidelines",
        "additional_details": "A lot of the nightlife workers have lost jobs and venues have shut causing A lot of illegal raves. This is harming communities people have been building for a long time.\r\n \r\nThe Government should support small venues and dance clubs by allowing under 350 capacity venues to reopen, with Covid-secure guidelines, including social distancing and other measures such as temperature checks and free hand sanitiser.\r\n\r\nPlease help our music industry.",
        "background": "DJs/Nightlife workers want to go back to Clubs/Venues to work. A lot of people have lost jobs and venues have shut permanently.\r\n \r\nThe Government should allow dance clubs and other venues with capacities of under 350 to reopen, with Covid-secure guidelines.",
